author: @batotit
text:
Things I noticed:
1. After watching lots of twice, Itzy, NMIXX, and even JYP dance practices, this room is very familiar to me now :D It is nice to see the edges. 

2. Dahyun is really the introvert of the group. It is not that she is aloof, but she prefers to be on her own most of the time. It is kinda surprising since she is always the one who is presented to be the eccentric weirdo in the group when they are being interviewed or in a reality game.

3. 9:46 Jungyoung is really closed to the trainer, and she is always the one talking to her, maybe even on behalf of the group.

4. I've always been a fan of nayeon and through her, I started following twice. All of them are really pretty. But Sana's beauty somehow is really blooming ever since "I can't stop me." I cant stop crushing on her. She is so handsome!

5. I'm a very cynical person, and I normally roll my eyes when artists give platitudes to other artists. It always feels so fake. But I'm really surprised that the members actually like each other and are real friends. You can see it in their interactions, not the smiling faces when they are on full-on camera, but the one in the background as they leaned tiredly toward each other.

text: Lately, I've been losing my interest in KPOP. I was in the phase wherein I felt everything wasn't the same as it was. I almost unstan Twice due to busy schedules I had in school. I had no time to watch videos or listen to their music. I'm currently in college and I'm so busy lately and I'm so stressed that every night I can't count how many tears I let go. But when I watched this video, the feelings I felt 7 years ago came back. It means I still love these girls 😭 Thank you again. You made my day happy even though I'm so stressed. You made me forget my problems in school, even just for a while. I thought no one could make me laugh rn😭 I love you girls! Stay Healthy!

text:
Ay, es tan lindo. Desde Sana con sus anecdotas y volando cual pajaro, Nayeon haciendo berrinches que nadie entiende, Momo queriendo experimentar lo que es "volar" como en el circo haha. Todas lo hacen tan genial, no pare de ver el esfuerzo de todas por aprender la coreo y dar una gran y pulcra presentación; Chae, Mina y Tzuyu tan lindas mientras se familiarizan con el compas de la canción. Jeon y Jihyo divirtiendose y gritando entre el baile y haciendo reir a los demás y Dahyun pidiendo con su ultimo aliento opinión sobre los pasos a llevar. <3 

Las AMO <3 Me hacen FELIZ y me pensar que puedo hacerlo MEJOR y que no solo hay amarguras en la vida sino también momentos como este donde puedes SONREIR, DISFRUTAR y sentirte QUERIDO-AMENO.
